    <metaDescription>
      <Value><![CDATA[QMU is dedicated to improving the quality of life and building the evidence-base for policy and practice development through research and knowledge exchange. We are highly regarded for innovative, relevant, practice and policy informing research and scholarship across a wide range of disciplines. The value of our work is measured by its impact and the social usefulness, practicality and applicability of its outcomes. Please find a copy of our Research Strategy 2015 - 2020.]]></Value>
